data.description: 4 year young- Open floor plan rancher on spacious, 5 acre lot. Minutes to Rappahannock River, Town of Tappahannock. Beautiful, distressed look LVP flooring. Split bedroom design.While no known defects, home is priced under market value to sell AS IS. Buyers are  welcome to do all customary inspections either required or desired at Buyers' sole expense. This will include well, septic and wood infestation inspections. Buyer will need to  arrange to have electric service temporarily restored for inspections.
